{"tid":1518234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大民調：11.2%受訪市民滿意特區政府表現","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:36:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":277,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"d97bde28d86547a956b4256d4caab96f3d52c267","tid":1518234,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:38:58.000Z","msg":"中大香港亞太研究所最新調查發現，特首林鄭月娥與律政司司長鄭若驊表現評分，與7月份比較均大幅下跌。林鄭月娥表現評分為28.4分，較7月下跌4.5分，比去年8月更是下跌27.8分；鄭若驊有20.3分，較7月下跌3.8分。<br />\n<br />\n另外兩名司長平均評分方面，政務司司長張建宗有32.9分，財政司司長陳茂波有29.8分，均較7月份下跌2.5分。<br />\n<br />\n調查結果又顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">11.2%受訪市民滿意特區政府表現</span>，不滿意的有65.5%；15.1%受訪市民信任北京中央政府，不信任的則有57.5%。<br />\n<br />\n電話調查在本月21至27日晚上進行，研究所成功訪問716名市民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477766-20190830.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477766-20190830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUii%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=73ba2c39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477766-20190830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2a9dbcc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477766-20190830.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a496ed3791ceb13acb499b15b21d47061dee0597","tid":1518234,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUii%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=c8fdd4fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c